data.description:
Welcome to this charming home, featuring 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom with an office space, a wonderful backyard, AND an additional back house!

Step inside, and be greeted by an updated interior. Every corner of this home exudes a sense of quality craftsmanship. The highlight of this property is the versatile office space, perfect for those who work remotely or desire a dedicated workspace.

This home boasts numerous updates. (Check the updates document for more information)

In addition to the main house, there is a fantastic back house, offering endless possibilities. Use it as a guest suite, a home gym, mother-in-law quarters, or as an income-generating rental unit. The versatility of this property is truly exceptional. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely property your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the endless possibilities it has to offer.
